comments: Holmgren (OKC) aligns to move alongside Mitchell's (CLE) path and marginal body contact occurs when they come together after Mitchell's gather.
Giddey (OKC) contests the put-back attempt and marginal contact occurs with Mobley's (CLE) right arm as Mobley finishes at the rim.
Mitchell's (CLE) right arm comes forward toward Dort's (OKC) path prior to marginal contact occurring with Mitchell's front/left arm at the end of the drive.
Holmgren (OKC) and Mobley (CLE) come together at the same spot as they move over the screen when marginal body contact occurs.
Mobley's (CLE) left arm slightly extends outward as he establishes his screening position and marginal contact occurs as Dort (OKC) goes over the pick.

Dort's (OKC) right hand comes forward in an attempt to dislodge the ball and marginal contact occurs with Mitchell's (CLE) head prior to the pass being released. Contact to an opponent's head/face can be deemed marginal when the result of a natural basketball move, provided the contact is not disproportionate or uncontrolled.
Holmgren's (OKC) upper body slightly extends forward as he braces for the impending contact with Mobley (CLE) and Holmgren absorbs the marginal contact as it occurs.

Replay review of the foul called on Holmgren (OKC) pursuant to a coach's challenge was deemed successful. Holmgren jumps with his right arm in a vertical position and cleanly blocks Mobley's (CLE) layup attempt as simultaneous incidental arm contact occurs. Oklahoma City was deemed to have imminent possession at the time of the whistle and was awarded possession following the review.
Okoro (CLE) engages and disengages with Joe (OKC) off-ball, and marginal contact occurs.
Holmgren (OKC) establishes himself in Wade's (CLE) path and does not deliver illegal contact.
Williams' (OKC) left hand moves forward toward Strus' (CLE) path and marginal contact occurs with Strus' front prior to Williams disengaging.
Williams' (OKC) right arm is brought forward when marginal contact occurs with Strus' (CLE) side/front after Strus gathers the pass and elevates for the layup.
Mobley (CLE) lands in front of Holmgren (OKC) following the shot contest and marginal contact occurs with Holmgren's slightly extended right foot as Holmgren returns to the floor.
Mobley (CLE) re-establishes his screening position slightly prior to marginal contact occurring with Dort (OKC) as the pick is set.
Dort (OKC) moves to align himself alongside Mitchell's (CLE) path and marginal body contact occurs as they come together at the end of Mitchell's drive.

Strus' (CLE) right hand comes forward toward Dort's (OKC) side and marginal contact occurs as Dort elevates for the driving shot attempt. Strus then brings his left arm into a vertical position prior to incidental arm contact occurring with Dort thereafter.
Dort (OKC) and Mitchell (CLE) mutually engage and disengage with one another during the inbound.
Dort (OKC) makes clean fingertip contact with the ball and blocks Mitchell's (CLE) jump shot attempt prior to the incidental contact with Mitchell's hand.
Mobley (CLE) initiates contact across both of Holmgren's (OKC) arms as he attempts to tie Holmgren up.
Strus' (CLE) is moving forward slightly prior to marginal contact occurring with Gilgeous-Alexander's (OKC) back after Gilgeous-Alexander receives the pass.
Mobley (CLE) moves toward Gilgeous-Alexander's (OKC) space and marginal body contact occurs prior to Gilgeous-Alexander passing the ball along the sideline.
Wade (CLE) makes clean forearm contact with the ball and dislodges it away from Giddey (OKC) as simultaneous marginal contact occurs with Giddey's back.
Okoro (CLE) commits a take foul on Williams (OKC).
Wiggins (OKC) legally contests Mitchell's (CLE) jump shot attempt.
Wade (CLE) initiates contact with Gilgeous-Alexander's (OKC) arm and upper body as he attempts to tie Gilgeous-Alexander up.
Gilgeous-Alexander's (OKC) right arm brushes Mitchell's (CLE) front and marginal contact occurs prior to Gilgeous-Alexander cleanly dislodging the ball away.
